additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Do not allow curtains or other flammable objects to contact the unit while it is in use. Handle electric device with dry hands only. When in use, do not touch with metal objects. Keep out of reach of children. Read safety directions. Young children should be supervised to ensure that they do not use or play with this device. Ensure device is not positioned close to children's cots and beds. Not intended for use by infirm persons without supervision. It should not be used in dining areas, food handling areas or food storage areas. Toxic to fish. Remove or cover fish tanks before use.
